# Optional AI Assist. Leave unset to run Canvas Studio with AI disabled.
# Point these at an endpoint YOU control that proxies to your LLM provider, so
# no API key is ever exposed in the browser. See docs/ai-endpoint.md.

# Base origin of your AI proxy, e.g. https://your-api.example.com
VITE_AI_API_ORIGIN=

# Request path on that origin (default: /api/canvas-ai)
# VITE_AI_API_PATH=/api/canvas-ai
